{"tid":1545924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推+幫手寄投訴信啊] 元朗天主教副校撕紙狗:「你係咪要屌呀？除褲啦！」","createTime":"2019-09-06T05:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:55:59.000Z","uid":86451,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"49aa420c62fe7b10710975acbf2ba74d2643bf48","tid":1545924,"uid":86451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"淨係推隔黎個po有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb有熱心人士打左template架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪餵到埋口都唔食先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n署名你打乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2153839114909618&amp;set=a.1392718677688336&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2153839114909618%26set%3Da.1392718677688336%26type%3D3%26theater&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=cb94e9de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2153839114909618&amp;set=a.1392718677688336&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n我再直接copy果個fb post既內容：<br />\n【集體投訴！元朗天主教中學陳秀芳副校長做撕紙狗兼爆粗事件】 原影片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kBBQIFRc5kY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkBBQIFRc5kY&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=d55ba406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kBBQIFRc5kY</a><br />\n以下投訴信歡迎使用：<br />\n<br />\n電郵：principal@ylcss.edu.hk ; hkcsco@catholic.org.hk ; sedoffice@edb.gov.hk ; psecsed@edb.gov.hk ; report@thestandnews.com ;<br />\n<br />\n電郵主題：投訴有關元朗天主教中學副校長陳秀芳女士有違教師專業操守事宜<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n<br />\n致：元朗天主教中學校長<br />\n抄送：天主教香港教區、教育局局長楊潤雄、教育局、立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n貴校任職副校長陳秀芳女士，於9月5日元朗水邊圍站的行人天橋，徒手破壞由市民籌建、以作和平表達政治訴求的「連儂牆」。當時一名途經的青年詢問陳女士為何蓄意破壞連儂牆，期間並無暴力行為，陳女士以粗言對罵回應，並繼續破壞。<br />\n<br />\n詳細情況見影片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kBBQIFRc5kY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkBBQIFRc5kY&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=d55ba406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kBBQIFRc5kY</a> (在約3分50秒，陳副校長說出一句：「你係咪要屌呀？除褲啦！」，令人譁然！)<br />\n<br />\n教師職責除了傳遞知識，更是從旁輔助學生選擇自己路向，並非將教師個人價值、政治意見強加於學生身上。同時，陳女士撕毀連儂牆的行為相信已觸犯《刑事罪行條例》第60條。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士的所作所為實在令人不齒，干犯法例之餘更有違教師專業操守與道德，令人質疑陳女士是否有能力勝任副校長的工作。望校長重新審視陳秀芳女士的副校長資格，秉公處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n本人已同時將事件抄送給天主教香港教區、教育局局長楊潤雄先生及傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\nXXX上"},{"pid":"1ee450567b5a7ef736d8528a8223487ae3402953","tid":1545924,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"813c20896e020c7b479fd8fd4b6cdd086d669d23","tid":1545924,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"黑警等清算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">九月八日 星期日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1:30pm遮打 ----&gt;  2pm美國領事館</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要絕對和理非，<br />\n控制場面！！！</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n颶風「多里安」<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逼近美國東岸在巴哈馬導致20人死亡</span></s