45924,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"應該要有學校嘅 &rdquo;持分者&rdquo; 先至可以落案 正式開file投訴<br />\n否則教育局都只會當係一般意見處理"},{"pid":"8e91fc772b6cb30bc3d6b4b52adf67bd6744c9db","tid":1545924,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:00:30.000Z","msg":"有冇呢間學校嘅學生或者家長願意企出嚟開名向教育局投訴？ 咁就會調查幾個月有排玩<br />\n係向教育局投訴<br />\n唔係向學校投訴<br />\n可以要求教育局將閣下嘅身份保密. 唔會畀學校知道報復<br />\n不過今時今日大家都信唔過政府了"},{"pid":"f6d71eae3fb3ad2f45efb1ffb251eb9b61068173","tid":1545924,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"利申： 玩過教育局投訴機制<br />\n如果匿名或者同學校冇關嘅人士投訴真係冇用的"},{"pid":"e2ac685c8ab204ad473b9e6a633fe51efec5248f","tid":1545924,"uid":276633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:02:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71160dbb18f0a9fca43fd10299d97dd5c995db6","tid":1545924,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af149b3fb1679074224fe83e400c356d7ece3c11","tid":1545924,"uid":4728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T23:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:14:52.000Z","msg":"你竟然仲相信政府唔會偏幫有立場嘅人"},{"pid":"d1451421e92b11b720ee922da7bde99f37479836","tid":1545924,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:44:33.000Z","msg":"條片死咗"}]}